from tqdm.notebook import tqdm
count=0
total=np.zeros(3)
total_2=np.zeros(3)
for i,fn in tqdm(enumerate(df['img_path']),'computing statistics...'):
  path = os.path.join('/', fn)
  imagearray = np.array(PIL.Image.open(os.path.join('/',fn)))/255
  if np.array(imagearray).shape[-1]==3:
    total += np.array(imagearray).reshape(-1,3).mean(axis=0)
    total_2 += ((np.array(imagearray).reshape(-1,3))**2).mean(axis=0)
    count+=1
channel_avr = total/count
channel_std = np.sqrt(total_2/count - channel_avr**2)

def create_databunch(val_idx,sz,bs):
  test = ImageList.from_df(test_df,path='/')
  data = (ImageList.from_df(df, path='/')
              .split_by_idx(val_idx)
              .label_from_df(cols='disease_class')
              .add_test(test)
              .transform(get_transforms(flip_vert=True), size=sz)
              .databunch(path='.', bs=bs)
              .normalize(imagenet_stats)
            )
  return data
